{"arkId":"cl010099071","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099071","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Commode \u00e0 deux vantaux","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Commode \u00e0 deux vantaux"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Premier Empire (1804-1814) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1805","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 553 - Valadier, Hors vitrine","room":"Salle 553, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1805,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"D\u00e9but du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Jacob, Fran\u00e7ois-Honor\u00e9-Georges dit Jacob-Desmalter","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1770","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1841","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Eb\u00e9niste","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q449885"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 9968","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"mobilier ; commode ; commode \u00e0 vantaux","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Commode \u00e0 pilastres en bois d\u2019acajou, dont le devant s\u2019ouvre \u00e0 deux portes sur chacune desquelles est un cadre cisel\u00e9 en feuilles d\u2019olivier avec des rosaces au milieu et aux angles. Dans l\u2019un des cadres, l\u0027Amour ; dans l\u2019autre, Psych\u00e9 tenant une \u00e9charpe flottante. Sur chacun des deux pilastres, un pi\u00e9destal orn\u00e9 d\u2019un bouquet de laurier portant un pied d\u2019ornement, surmont\u00e9 d\u2019un vase antique, avec flamme et guirlande de retomb\u00e9e. Le devant de la ceinture est orn\u00e9 d\u2019une guirlande de feuilles de ch\u00eane, se terminant en anneau \u00e0 chaque bout et formant m\u00e9daillon repr\u00e9sentant l\u2019une une t\u00eate de guerrier, l\u2019autre une t\u00eate de reine. Au-dessus de la guirlande, un bas-relief repr\u00e9sentant un char de triomphe entre deux chevaux marins. Sur chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 de la ceinture, une grande rosace aec deux cornets \u00e0 anses et t\u00eate de sanglier. La corniche est orn\u00e9e de palmettes et de perles, et l\u2019ar\u00eate inf\u00e9rieure de ladite ceinture, garnie d\u2019un filet uni. Tout au pourtour sur chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 de la commode, un cornet avec accompagnement d\u2019ornements arabesques. Le dessus est en marbre blanc vein\u00e9.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; C. 317. C (Inventaire de 1894)\r ; C 565 (MArque \u00e0 l\u0027encre (inventaire de 1855))\r ; ELB (sans n\u00b0)  (marque au fer rouge)\r ; 999 (\u00e9tiquette imprim\u00e9e, inventaire de 1938)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,165","displayDimension":"1,165 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"1,794","displayDimension":"1,794 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,83","displayDimension":"0,83 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : acajou\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bronze (dor\u00e9)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Provenant du grand salon de la grande chambre de Napol\u00e9on Ier \u00e0 l\u0027Elys\u00e9e : inventaire du mobilier de l\u0027Elys\u00e9e en 1809, n\u00b0 100 (O\u00b2 705 f\u00b0 29 v\u00b0) ; entr\u00e9 au palais de Compi\u00e8gne post\u00e9rieurement \u00e0 1848 (inventaire de 1855, n\u00b0 565) ; d\u00e9p\u00f4t du mus\u00e9e national du ch\u00e2teau de Compi\u00e8gne au d\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art le 13 novembre 1957, \u00e0 la suite d\u0027un \u00e9change contre les deux consoles de Benneman (OA 5442 et OA 5443)","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"d\u00e9p\u00f4t","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"13\/11\/1957","startYear":1957,"endYear":1957}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"d\u00e9p\u00f4t"}],"period":[{"value":"Premier Empire (1804-1814)"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"}],"objectType":[{"value":"mobilier"},{"value":"commode"},{"value":"commode \u00e0 vantaux"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000099071\/0000243851_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000099071\/0000243851_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000099071\/0000243846_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000099071\/0000243846_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000099071\/0000243847_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000099071\/0000243847_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":2},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cach